snippet: Since joining the Big Ten last year, the top-ranked Maryland women’s lacrosse team has received more attention and has bolstered the conference’s reputation in the sport.
abstract: Ohio State defeats Maryland, 11-10, in semifinals of inaugural Big Ten women's lacrosse championship; Maryland, at 17-1, receives top overall seed in NCAA tournament.
lead_paragraph: Since joining the Big Ten last year, the top-ranked Maryland women’s lacrosse team has received more attention and has bolstered the conference’s reputation in the sport.

headline.main: Maryland Women, in Big Ten, Find Exposure for Their Lacrosse Dominance
headline.print_headline: Maryland Women Seize Stage in Big Ten
